    Checks whether a domain name in the cloudapp.net zone is available for use.

    Task<AzureOperationResponse<DnsNameAvailabilityResult>> CheckDnsNameAvailabilityWithHttpMessagesAsync(string location, string domainNameLabel = null, Dictionary<string, List<string>> customHeaders = null, CancellationToken cancellationToken = null)Function CheckDnsNameAvailabilityWithHttpMessagesAsync(location As String, domainNameLabel As String = Nothing, customHeaders As Dictionary(Of String, List(Of String)) = Nothing, cancellationToken As CancellationToken = Nothing) As Task(Of AzureOperationResponse(Of DnsNameAvailabilityResult))

    Parameters

    • location
      String
      String

      The location of the domain name.

    • domainNameLabel
      String
      String

      The domain name to be verified. It must conform to the following regular expression: ^[a-z][a-z0-9-]{1,61}[a-z0-9]$.
